         <div class="featured-boxes">
          <div class="panel-panel panel-top-four featured-box">
           <div class="inside">
            <div class="panel-pane pane-fieldable-panels-pane pane-fpid-3 pane-bundle-home-box">
             <h2 class="pane-title">
              <a href="https://epic.uchicago.in/">
               EPIC-India
              </a>
              <img alt="right arrow" src="/sites/all/themes/epic_theme/images/home-feature-right-arrow.png"/>
             </h2>
             <div class="fieldable-panels-pane">
              <img alt="" class="home-boxes-284-x-164" height="256" src="https://epic.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/home_boxes_284_x_164/public/India-home-thumb.jpg?itok=xwf9_x-E" typeof="foaf:Image" width="443"/>
              <div class="field field--name-field-home-box-featured-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden">
               <div class="field__items">
                <div class="field__item even">
                 <p>
                  The India team at the Energy Policy Institute at the University of Chicago (EPIC-India) works to expand access to reliable and affordable energy, identify low-cost solutions to reduce pollution, and improve human health and productivity. It does so by working hand-in-hand with government and industry partners to identify innovative ideas, pilot them on the ground, and rigorously measure outcomes. This approach ensures the right questions are being answered, and results can be scaled up into lasting policy changes.
                 </p>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
              <div class="field field--name-field-home-box-featured-link field--type-link-field field--label-hidden">
               <div class="field__items">
                <div class="field__item even">
                 <a href="https://epic.uchicago.in/">
                  Read More ...
                 </a>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-panel panel-bottom-four featured-box">
           <div class="inside">
            <div class="panel-pane pane-fieldable-panels-pane pane-uuid-ab9564f8-ba0c-457c-a50c-cdab614f1f5c pane-bundle-home-box">
             <h2 class="pane-title">
              <a href="https://urbanlabs.uchicago.edu/labs/energy-environment">
               Urban Energy, Environment Lab
              </a>
              <img alt="right arrow" src="/sites/all/themes/epic_theme/images/home-feature-right-arrow.png"/>
             </h2>
             <div class="fieldable-panels-pane">
              <img alt="" class="home-boxes-284-x-164" height="256" src="https://epic.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/home_boxes_284_x_164/public/urbanlabs-home-thumb_1.jpg?itok=q53R0A7p" typeof="foaf:Image" width="443"/>
              <div class="field field--name-field-home-box-featured-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden">
               <div class="field__items">
                <div class="field__item even">
                 <p>
                  The Urban Energy &amp; Environment Lab is one of five labs focused on identifying and testing the most promising urban policies to confront our greatest challenges. Through an Innovation Challenge that solicits ideas from the community, the lab will test the winning ideas to guide successful energy policies that can be implemented nationally and internationally.
                 </p>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
              <div class="field field--name-field-home-box-featured-link field--type-link-field field--label-hidden">
               <div class="field__items">
                <div class="field__item even">
                 <a href="https://urbanlabs.uchicago.edu/labs/energy-environment">
                  Read More...
                 </a>
                </div>
